snippet.title: Best VGM 884 - Deadly Premonition - Life is Beautiful
snippet.description:
Fast and Low-Pitched version: https://youtu.be/YZm0dapv_mw

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Xbox 360
Deadly Premonition (2010)
Life is Beautiful
Riyou Kinugasa, Takuya Kobayashi & Hiromi Mizutani
